votes:
Amazing Cast, Talented, Interesting and sophisticated individuals. 'Imzy' Imran Cummings, Jibril Rose, Mei-li Jade, Devonyae Headley, Brad Kent, Mustapha Jabang alongside Ed Acura and the team really delivered on this series and effectively highlighted a systemic issue that's plagued our country and westernised societies for generations. It's time for change.

It explores the life of Imran Cummings (Imzy) and Mei-Li Jade with the narrative centered around them; alongside supporting cast such as Imzy's friends and people they interact with in regular day-to day activities. International elements are also included such as the Portugal part later on in the series where Jibril rose and Imzy were flown out and captured some of their experiences especially those around water.

Overall, a great watch with an impact left for generations and we're excited to see what the future holds for these talented artists, actors, poets, social media stars, etc.
